sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant B as Browser/CLI
    participant S as Server

    Note over U,S:CREATE PASTE
    U->>B:Text/File + Password (or empty for auto-generated)
    B->>B:Generate salt(16B) + nonce(12B)
    B->>B:master = Argon2id(password, salt, 32B)
    B->>B:enc_key = HKDF(master, "mitsuzo-encryption-key")
    B->>B:val_key = HKDF(master, "mitsuzo-validation-key")
    B->>B:hash = HMAC-SHA256(val_key, salt)
    B->>B:Encrypt chunks with ChaCha20-Poly1305(enc_key)
    Note right of B:Derived nonce = base_nonce XOR chunk_index
    B->>S:POST /api/paste [framed: header + encrypted_chunks]
    Note right of S:Stores: files/{id} + files/{id}.nonce
Sled DB: pass, salt, meta
    S->>B:Return paste ID

    Note over U,S:VIEW PASTE
    U->>B:Paste ID + Password (from URL #hash)
    B->>S:GET /api/paste/{id}/salt
    S->>B:Return {salt, try_count, ttl, total_chunks}
    B->>B:Re-derive keys (Argon2id + HKDF)
    B->>B:hash = HMAC-SHA256(val_key, salt)
    B->>S:GET /api/paste/{id} + X-Password-Hash
    alt Hash matches (constant-time compare)
        S->>B:Framed: GetPasteHeader + encrypted_chunks
        B->>B:Decrypt chunks with derived nonce
        B->>U:Display plaintext / Download file
    else Hash mismatch
        S->>S:try_count--
        S->>S:if try_count==0, delete paste
        S->>B:401 Unauthorized
    end
